public static final int[] CirclePageIndicator
Attributes that can be used with a CirclePageIndicator.

Includes the following attributes:

AttributeDescription
android:background View background
android:orientation Orientation of the indicator.
org.apps8os.motivator:centered Whether or not the indicators should be centered.
org.apps8os.motivator:fillColor Color of the filled circle that represents the current page.
org.apps8os.motivator:pageColor Color of the filled circles that represents pages.
org.apps8os.motivator:radius Radius of the circles.
org.apps8os.motivator:snap Whether or not the selected indicator snaps to the circles.
org.apps8os.motivator:strokeColor Color of the open circles.
org.apps8os.motivator:strokeWidth Width of the stroke used to draw the circles.

public static final int[] TitlePageIndicator
Attributes that can be used with a TitlePageIndicator.

Includes the following attributes:

AttributeDescription
android:background View background
android:textColor Color of regular titles.
android:textSize Size of title text.
org.apps8os.motivator:clipPadding Screen edge padding.
org.apps8os.motivator:footerColor Color of the footer line and indicator.
org.apps8os.motivator:footerIndicatorHeight Height of the indicator above the footer line.
org.apps8os.motivator:footerIndicatorStyle Style of the indicator.
org.apps8os.motivator:footerIndicatorUnderlinePadding Left and right padding of the underline indicator.
org.apps8os.motivator:footerLineHeight Height of the footer line.
org.apps8os.motivator:footerPadding Padding between the bottom of the title and the footer.
org.apps8os.motivator:linePosition Position of the line.
org.apps8os.motivator:selectedBold Whether or not the selected item is displayed as bold.
org.apps8os.motivator:selectedColor Color of the selected title.
org.apps8os.motivator:titlePadding Padding between titles when bumping into each other.
org.apps8os.motivator:topPadding Padding between titles and the top of the View.
